edu.stanford.services.explorecourses

Class Course

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.stanford.services.explorecourses.Course

  • public class Course
extends java.lang.Object
    Courses are specified using a subject code (eg: CS140, CS161, CS343), and have properties like a title (eg: "Introduction to Operating Systems") and description. A Course may be taught zero or more times in any given academic year, and each instance of the class is called a "Section".
